NORTH LEADING LIVE EXPERIENCE AMERICA'S FIRM F ifth Element Group is an award winning live experience firm, recognized worldwide as a leading creative force in large scale galas & events, fundraisers, conference management, design and live activations. For over 20 years we have created and managed event environments for the world's top brands, companies and philanthropic efforts. Executing on our promise for industry leading creativity and customer service is our daily mission with a team of influential and passionate event professionals who continue to raise the bar in the field of live experiences. Our work has influenced campaigns, gatherings, fundraisers, conferences and even celebrity weddings and we do that with attention to detail, passion and a vision for one team, endless possibilities & creative original results. LIVE EXPERIENCE IDEATION, CREATION & EXECUTION DIGITAL AND ONLINE EVENT SOLUTIONS COMPLETE EVENT SOLUTIONS & MANAGEMENT EVENT DESIGN MARKETING ACTIVATIONS AND SAMPLING SPONSORSHIP ACQUISITION & MANAGEMENT CUSTOM BRAND EXPERIENCES INTERNATIONAL MEETINGS, EVENTS AND SUMMITS TALENT / ARTIST PROCUREMENT & MANAGEMENT SERVICES WHAT WE DO We have established industry relationships and partnerships that not only deliver top-notch service, but also provide unmatched competitive pricing to lower our clients’ bottom-line. We work with top tiered vendors across the country and internationally. Services "We produce with passion and relentless creativity. Our team, understands the meaning of vision from beginning to end" THE EVENTS @fifthelementgrp #fifthelementgrp The Events Fifth Element Group is an award winning live experience firm, recognized worldwide as a leading creative force in design, large scale events, conference management and live activations.
